Class BaseObjectiveProblem

java.lang.Object
  cz.cvut.felk.cig.jcop.problem.BaseObjectiveProblem
All Implemented Interfaces:
DestinationProblem, GlobalSearchProblem, ObjectiveProblem, Problem, RandomConfigurationProblem, StartingConfigurationProblem
public final class BaseObjectiveProblem
extends java.lang.Object
implements ObjectiveProblem

This class should be base for all problems (at least local search problems) implemented.

Constructor Detail

BaseObjectiveProblem

public BaseObjectiveProblem(Problem problem)
Creates new BaseObjectiveProblem which wraps around supplied problem.

BaseObjectiveProblem emulates all problem interfaces by redirecting method calls to problem (if it implements such interface) or throws an exception (if it does not).

Parameters:
problem - problem to have BaseObjectiveProblem wrapped around

public OperationIterator getOperationIterator(Configuration configuration)
Description copied from interface: Problem
Returns iterator for operations which are allowed for supplied attributes.
